0.3.name: wordpress/facebook-image-fix
0.3.description: FaceBook Image Fix solves problem with FaceBook LikeIt and Share actions. Sometimes when you share/like one of yours pages can happen that images viewed in FaceBook are wrong. This plugin solves the problem by inserting FaceBook Open Graph or XFBML Tag. Easy configuration! Seo Plugin support!
